{"questionId":"11774","questionHtml":"<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Adesh wants to model the cooling of a metal rod. He heats the rod and records its temperature as it cools.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\"><img src=\"__IMG__/dc3df2bca8961d737b21e2d9332e61c01d58dcad.png\"></p>\n<p>He believes the temperature can be modeled by&nbsp;<span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"T\\left( t \\right) = a{{\\text{e}}^{bt}} + 25\">\n  <mi>T</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mo>(</mo>\n    <mi>t</mi>\n    <mo>)</mo>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>e</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n      <mrow>\n        <mi>b</mi>\n        <mi>t</mi>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>+</mo>\n  <mn>25</mn>\n</math></span>, where <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a{\\text{,}}\\,\\,b \\in \\mathbb{R}\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mrow>\n    <mtext>,</mtext>\n  </mrow>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mo>∈</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <mi mathvariant=\"double-struck\">R</mi>\n  </mrow>\n</math></span>.</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-parent-stem\"><p>Hence</p></div>\n<div class=\"qb-leaf-prompt\"><p>find the value of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n</math></span>&nbsp;and of <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b\">\n  <mi>b</mi>\n</math></span>.</p></div>","markschemeHtml":"<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"b =&nbsp; - 0.00870\">\n  <mi>b</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mo>−</mo>\n  <mn>0.00870</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"a = {e^{3.89...}} = 49.1\">\n  <mi>a</mi>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mrow>\n    <msup>\n      <mi>e</mi>\n      <mrow>\n        <mn>3.89...</mn>\n      </mrow>\n    </msup>\n  </mrow>\n  <mo>=</mo>\n  <mn>49.1</mn>\n</math></span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>M1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"11774","referenceCode":"EXM.1.AHL.TZ0.15c.i","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"find the value of a and of b .","paper":"1","level":"HL","questionNumber":"c.i","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 2—Functions","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","Topic 4—Statistics and probability","SL 4.4—Pearsons, scatter diagrams, eqn of y on x","Topic 2—Functions","AHL 2.10—Scaling large numbers, log-log graphs"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}